<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1986—Pars. (1), (3). <ref href="/us/pl/99/640">Pub. L. 99–640</ref> struck out “owned by a citizen of the United States” after “vessel”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1984—Par. (4). <ref href="/us/pl/98/364">Pub. L. 98–364</ref>, as amended <ref href="/us/pl/98/557">Pub. L. 98–557</ref>, added par. (4).</p>
</note>
